Subject: Re: [T2] '79 Door on '74 Bus?

Hi Vincent,

There is a way that it can be done.

If you pull the pin out of both hinges the late door hinge will mate 
fine with the early door hinge. Put the pin back in and you're good to 
go.

Happy trails,

