On 2-Mar-04, at 9:56 AM, Vincent Molenaar wrote:

>> Can anyone give a catagorical answer on whether I
>> can just bolt the '79
>> door into the '74?
>
> You can't. On 1977-1979 MODELyears the hinges are
> different than the hinges used in 1968-1976.
>
> 1968-1976: (hinge)bolt screws into piece of metal
> welded to the body
>
> 1977-1979: (hinge)bolt screws into hinge
